title: 383A.291 CERTIFICATION OF ELIGIBLES.
text:
MS 1996 [Repealed, 1997 c 40 s 2]
Upon request of the appointing authority, the human resources director shall certify eligibles in accordance with rules adopted under section 383A.284, subdivision 1.
